data.title: Dave Campbell's Texas Football
data.meta_description: Get the latest news and information about the Stockdale Brahmas football from Dave Campbell's Texas Football.
data.text:
Tepper's picks for the best all across Texas...

Only 17 Texas high school football teams out of 1,500 fit the mold...

Locker room technology, horse collar tackles, field goal blocks among the rule changes coming to UIL Texas high school football this season.

College and high school coaches spanning the Lone Star State are honored.

Greg Tepper and Matt Stepp nerd out on the 2024 Texas State 7-on-7 Tournament in College Station in this Insiders-only podcast, including breakdowns of every division and predictions for the champions.

Greg Tepper and Matt Stepp nerd out on the Texas high school football offseason in this Insiders-only podcast, discussing coaching changes and a way-too-early look at the 2024 season.
